comments: Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly engages with Butler (PHI) but does not affect his ability to defend the pass.
Butler (PHI) legally contests Antetokounmpo's (MIL) shot near the rim.
RAR shows Antetokounmpo (MIL) beats Simmons (PHI) to the spot and the contact is marginal.
Redick (PHI) is already in Antetokounmpo's (MIL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Embiid (PHI) draws Lopez (MIL) into the air towards him, which results in a foul on Lopez even if contact is initiated by Embiid.
[Observable in enhanced video] Antetokounmpo (MIL) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Simmons (PHI) makes contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm as he defends the shot near the rim.
Embiid (PHI) is already in Bledsoe's (MIL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
RAR and LAR show Lopez (MIL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Embiid's (PHI) shot attempt.
Middleton (MIL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Harris (PHI) that does not affect his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Harris (PHI) slides his foot at the start of the dribble.
Butler (PHI) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) that does not affect his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Antetokounmpo (MIL) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Butler (PHI) does not maintain legal guarding position and he makes contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) body that affects his shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) maintains his pivot foot after his gather.
Lopez (MIL) maintains legal guarding position and makes marginal  contact with Embiid (PHI) in the backcourt.

LAR shows Lopez (MIL) deflects the ball and the ball touches the sideline, possession is correctly awarded to PHI.  After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor (76ers ball) was confirmed.
Connaughton (MIL) commits a take foul on Butler (PHI).
Simmons (PHI) does not make contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm as he defends his driving shot attempt.
Bledsoe (MIL) commits a take foul on Butler (PHI).
Middleton (MIL) commits a take foul on Embiid (PHI).
Middleton (MIL) and Embiid (PHI) briefly engage and separate during the inbound.
Lopez (MIL) commits a take foul on Harris (PHI).
Mirotic (MIL) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
